 9/3/18 La Bass Vill of our 18 rounder shell had been fall short . Left here and return down a railway track come out at the C.T. which is a good one . A long trudg down this trench and we met stretcher bearer return from carri out case . Call in at the R.A.P and found that various slight wound chap had pass through there . Our communic trench had been blown in at various place dure enemi retali . Our chap on the left flank told me that dure our barrag they could hear cri come from the German post opposit them . We have lost some good chap tonight . After return to Bn H.Q . rest a while
